{"tid":39622,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"原來90後係無分種族，今日比隻90後死黑鬼打左巴......","createTime":"2016-12-14T16:26:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T05:12:27.000Z","uid":19334,"like":6,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d4a7d515d4bc50533efbcd6a5a9be251ce8db240","tid":39622,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T16:26:19.000Z","msg":"呢排男朋友好忙，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔得閒收工接我，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我多左去公司樓下個巴士站搭巴士返屋企，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日唔知發生咩事好多外籍人士，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有d仲要幾靚仔，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁呢d望下就算，我呢d毒絲，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁無啦啦有隻死90後黑鬼用唔咸唔淡既廣東話問我，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「良景村點去，beauty！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我見佢咁口乖咪答佢囉，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原本想答佢搭58X，總站落就得，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知話口未完架58X就到，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我咪大大聲話「呢架，Go」！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知佢無啦啦一巴車埋黎，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係痴撚線！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後佢就急急腳咁走左！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家d 90後真係有病，好心著雷劈！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d63c6392baa610681e0acfd894f6691b12e2657c","tid":39622,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":